# Automated Young's Modulus calculation

Click the green arrow below or Ctrl+Alt+R to perform Young's Modulus calculation for all bone Stress/Strain in the "data" folder!

All results are saved in the "results/youngs-modulus" folder. See the README in that folder for a detailed description of its contents.


```{r}
source("./src/script/youngsModulus/automatedCalculation.R")
entry()
```
